data.description: Discover Serenity In This Secluded 4-5 Bed, 3 Bath One-level Country Home On 2.5+ Open Acres. Inside, Updates Abound, Featuring Fresh Paint, Flooring, Led Fixtures/fans, Kitchen Appliances, Landscaping, And An Expanded Living/dining Area. The Split Floor Plan Places The Primary Bedroom With A Large En Suite Bath On One Side, While Three Additional Bedrooms Occupy The Other. You'll Also Find A Large Circular Concrete Driveway With Ample Parking Along With An Attached 2-car Garage And Outbuilding. Embrace Outdoor Living And Only Nature Around With A Covered Front Porch And Two Spacious Back Patio Areas. All Of That And Just 10 Minutes From Court Square And Other Local Hot Spots. Added Bonus: Seller Providing A One-year Home Warranty!
